name: @grpc/grpc-js

scripts.format: clang-format -i -style="{Language: JavaScript, BasedOnStyle: Google, ColumnLimit: 80}" src/*.ts test/*.ts
scripts.generate-test-types: proto-loader-gen-types --keepCase --longs String --enums String --defaults --oneofs --includeComments --include-dirs test/fixtures/ -O test/generated/ --grpcLib ../../src/index test_service.proto
scripts.generate-types: proto-loader-gen-types --keepCase --longs String --enums String --defaults --oneofs --includeComments --includeDirs proto/ --include-dirs test/fixtures/ -O src/generated/ --grpcLib ../index channelz.proto
scripts.prepare: npm run generate-types && npm run compile
scripts.pretest: npm run generate-types && npm run generate-test-types && npm run compile
